Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • accounts.Account
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SavingsAccount

    public class Account
extends java.lang.Object
    Account object has 4 attributes: - id - unique id of Account, - accountName - name of account, - accountBalance - account balance, - expensesList - ArrayList of expenses.
